beer.beer_name: Cirta Ostara | New World Pale Ale
beer.beer_description: Cirta Ostara is a celebration of new beginnings. Named for the spring equinox goddess. This new world pale, brewed with a generous dose of Citra hops is bursting with juicy citrus, mango, and a hint of pine. A crisp malt backbone and dry finish make it the perfect toast to longer days & lighter vibes.
